<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Reminder - Invoice {{invoiceNumber}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background-color: #fee2e2;
            border: 2px solid #ef4444;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .alert-box h2 {
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .invoice-summary {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .invoice-summary table {
            width: 100%;
        }
        .invoice-summary td {
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        .amount-due {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ef4444;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .consequences {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            color: #856404;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Payment Reminder</h1>
            <p style="margin: 5px 0;">Invoice {{invoiceNumber}} is Overdue</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="alert-box">
                <h2>Your invoice is {{daysOverdue}} days overdue</h2>
                <p>Please make payment as soon as possible to avoid service interruption.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="invoice-summary">
                <h3>Invoice Details</h3>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Invoice Number:</strong></td>
                        <td>{{invoiceNumber}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Issue Date:</strong></td>
                        <td>{{formatDate issueDate}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Due Date:</strong></td>
                        <td style="color: #ef4444; font-weight: bold;">{{formatDate dueDate}}</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Days Overdue:</strong></td>
                        <td style="color: #ef4444; font-weight: bold;">{{daysOverdue}} days</td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
            
            <div class="amount-due">
                Amount Due: ${{formatNumber total}}
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{paymentUrl}}" class="button">Pay Now</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="consequences">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0;">Important Notice</h4>
                <p>If payment is not received within the next 48 hours:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Your services may be temporarily suspended</li>
                    <li>Late fees may be applied to your account</li>
                    <li>Access to AI bots and APIs will be restricted</li>
                </ul>
                <p><strong>Avoid service disruption by paying today.</strong></p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 30px;">
                <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1976d2;">Need Help?</h4>
                <p>If you're experiencing difficulties with payment or have questions about this invoice:</p>
                <ul style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                    <li>Contact our billing team at <a href="mailto:billing@logos-ecosystem.com">billing@logos-ecosystem.com</a></li>
                    <li>Call us at +1 (555) 123-4567</li>
                    <li>Chat with support at <a href="https://logos-ecosystem.com/support">logos-ecosystem.com/support</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Thank you for your immediate attention to this matter.</strong></p>
            <p>
                LOGOS Ecosystem | 123 AI Street, San Francisco, CA 94105<br>
                <a href="https://logos-ecosystem.com">logos-ecosystem.com</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px;">
                This is an automated reminder. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>